title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAR-25-2014 TUES

The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAR-25-2014 TUES...PODCAST


The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET


   
      
      The Glenn Beck Program 3/25/14Tuesday, March 25, 2014 




Glenn talks about what China and Russia have planned for the United States

 and predicts Russia's next moves.


 Later, he sheds light on the absurdities of common core math 
    and covers the latest on the Hobby Lobby Supreme Court case.

 Chris McDaniel joins the the program to discuss his run for Senate.

 That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!
